5 Section 5. The following KRS sections are repealed:
6 158.170 Bible to be read.
7 158.177 Teaching of evolution -- Right to include Bible theory of creation.
8 158.178 Ten Commandments to be displayed.
9 Section 6. This Act shall be cited as the Student Secular Bill of Rights.
